description: After two nights of live launch shows to introduce the 16 housemates, the highlights programmes begin. They follow the first lot of contestants as they wake up to their first full day in their new surroundings and also show them welcoming the second intake on Friday evening - when Big Brother had a special decision for Pauline, who had been voted as the most powerful housemate
